My friend and I ordered the restaurant's new Set 3 (which included grilled ribs, hot pot, and a complimentary drink) for two people. I found this set to have quite a lot of food, and the side dishes were also plentiful. The meat was fresh and of good quality. They even had staff to grill it for us, which was great!

Seoseo BBQ Restaurant is truly one of the culinary places that has impressed me the most recently, and is completely worthy of a full 5-star rating. From the moment I stepped into the restaurant, I felt the meticulousness in the arrangement …
